INSTALLATION STEPS:

Install Python 3.6.4 from https://www.python.org/downloads/
Install Cython (e.g. sudo -H pip3 install Cython==0.26.1)
Install Kivy v1.10.1.dev0 (e.g. sudo -H pip3 install https://github.com/kivy/kivy/archive/master.zip)
Install pyrebase (e.g. sudo -H pip3 install pyrebase)


TO UPGRADE PIP:
pip install --upgrade pip